OL,3,CStarmer vows to curb 'Nimby' court
OL,4,Cbattles over major infrastructure
OL,5,Cprojects
OL,7,FOpponents of major infrastructure
OL,8,Fprojects will have fewer chances to
OL,9,F"frustrate growth" through repeated
OL,10,Flegal challenges, the prime minister
OL,11,Fhas said.
OL,13,FSir Keir Starmer said he would end a
OL,14,F"challenge culture" that saw major
OL,15,Fprojects such as nuclear power plants,
OL,16,Fwind farms and roads delayed by
OL,17,Funarguable bids for judicial review.
