OL,7,FNumber 10 said the changes would
OL,8,Fprevent "cynical" or "hopeless" cases
OL,9,Fcausing delays and increasing the cost
OL,10,Fof infrastructure projects.
OL,12,FOpponents currently have three
OL,13,Fopportunities to secure permission for
OL,14,Fa judicial review against a major
OL,15,Finfrastructure project ` firstly by
OL,16,Fwriting to the High Court, then in an
OL,17,Foral hearing and finally by asking the
OL,18,FCourt of Appeal.
