OL,7,FBut under plans announced by the prime
OL,8,Fminister on Thursday, the written
OL,9,Fstage will be scrapped and any cases
OL,10,Fdeemed "totally without merit" will be
OL,11,Funable to ask the Court of Appeal to
OL,12,Freconsider.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FStarmer said that for too long
OL,20,Fblockers "have had the upper hand in
OL,21,Flegal challenges".
