OL,7,F"We're putting an end to this
OL,8,Fchallenge culture by taking on the
OL,9,FNimbys and a broken system that has
OL,10,Fslowed down our progress as a nation.
OL,12,F"This is the Government's Plan for
OL,13,FChange in action ` taking the brakes
OL,14,Foff Britain by reforming the planning
OL,15,Fsystem so it is pro-growth and pro-
OL,16,Finfrastructure."
