OL,7,FWriting in the Daily Mail, the prime
OL,8,Fminister said: "Cases that are
OL,9,Funarguable and unwinnable can be
OL,10,Fbrought back to the courts three
OL,11,Ftimes. That causes years of delay. It
OL,12,Fcosts hundreds of millions of pounds.
OL,13,FIt clogs up the courts. And strangles
OL,14,Fgrowth.
OL,16,F"The entire country pays the price.
