OL,4,Cbattles over major infrastructure
OL,5,Cprojects
OL,7,F"Bringing back common sense to
OL,8,Fbuilding is the least this country
OL,9,Fdeserves. Because if we want growth,
OL,10,Fwe need the infrastructure to support
OL,11,Fit."
OL,13,FThe government has already committed
OL,14,Fto making 150 major infrastructure
OL,15,Fproject decisions by the next
OL,16,Felection, and on Wednesday announced
OL,17,Fchanges to environmental protection
OL,18,Frules to speed up building work.
