OL,7,FLord Banner said he was "pleased to
OL,8,Fsee the government acting on the back
OL,9,Fof my review", adding that "reducing
OL,10,Fthe number of permission attempts to
OL,11,Fone for truly hopeless cases should
OL,12,Fweed out the worst offenders".
OL,14,FAccording to the government, more than
OL,15,Fhalf of decisions on nationally
OL,16,Fsignificant infrastructure projects
OL,17,Fwere taken to court, causing an
OL,18,Faverage delay of 18 months and adding
OL,19,Fmillions to costs.
